title: Ah mate this game is so good actually
body:
Yeah man, I guess no one is playing this game anymore, 10-20 minute queues for normal draft modes during 12pm-11pm. 
And then when I get people I have pre level 30's on my team that are so delusional you could say it borders on mental illness. While I have to play against a season 7 challenger player who one tricks Jayce and was RANK 13 really good. 

Really good

replies.body:
m8 dont know what game your playing but getting is 10-20 min qs at 12pm - 11pm is never happening for me.

also you should know by now that those times are scuffed times and you get the most bacterial players ever

> Yeah man, I guess no one is playing this game anymore, 10-20 minute queues for normal draft modes during 12pm-11pm.

Well people have job, daily life to attend to. What do you want them to be? gamers without any responsibilities in the real world? Stay up late to entertain you and yours?
